article_title: IPO Pricing Values e-Commerce Group Zalando at Up to €5.6 Billion
article_text:
FRANKFURT—Zalando SE on Wednesday set the price range for shares in its initial public offering, valuing the German e-commerce company at up to 5.6 billion euros ($7.25 billion).

The fashion retailer said it could raise as much as €633 million by selling 11.3% of its shares, including a green-shoe option. The price range for shares in the IPO is...
